          <li><strong>Update</strong> your OS, browser, and apps automatically.</li>
          <li><strong>Think before you click</strong>‚Äîverify unexpected links/attachments.</li>
          <li><strong>Back up</strong> important files to the cloud and an external drive.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="subtitle">These five habits block the majority of common attacks like credential stuffing, phishing, and ransomware.</p>
      </div>
