      <span class="kicker">How Hacks Happen</span>
      <h2>How Hacks Happen</h2>
      <p>Hacks often begin with phishing emails, weak passwords, or outdated software that attackers exploit. Social engineering techniques trick users into giving away access without realizing it.</p>
    </section>

