<section id="protect" class="card" role="region" aria-labelledby="protect-title">
  <span class="kicker">Protect Yourself</span>
  <h2 id="protect-title">How to Protect Yourself</h2>
  <ul class="checklist">
    <li tabindex="0">Use strong, unique passwords with a password manager</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Turn on two-factor authentication (2FA)</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Keep your device and apps up to date</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Avoid clicking on suspicious links or attachments</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Back up your important files regularly</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Use secure and private Wi-Fi networks; avoid public Wi-Fi when possible</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Install reputable antivirus and anti-malware software</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Be cautious about sharing personal info on social media</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Regularly review privacy and security settings on apps and devices</li>
    <li tabindex="0">Learn to recognize phishing scams and suspicious emails</li>
  </ul>
</section>

